extendedInfo.description: Mobile conference app for the 2013 YP Summit, bringing together 1,500 young professionals, business and community leaders for the largest young professionals event in the region. Artist, performer and philanthropist John Legend headlines the conference, with opening speaker and founder of Pencils of Promise, Adam Braun, and a long slate of breakout sessions converge with community partners and co-creators for the most unique and inspirational opportunity in the Midwest. Held in Omaha, Nebraska on February 28 at the CenturyLink Center - Omaha, young professionals can?t afford to miss it! @omahayp #ypsummit #transformation Conference app includes: + Conference program + Breakout session guide + Attendee ?transformer? list + Co-creator living room maps + Conference location, parking, closest bus stops & after-party infoKeywords: Omaha, young, professionals, YP, Summit, CenturyLink Center, Nebraska, Chamber, Greater Omaha Chamber, Conference, transformation, Midwest
